data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: Because Windows stores the colors in an array in the registry. Windows Controls adapt colors from this array in dark mode in a different way to light mode, and Windows does that to assure that controls have contrast and can be seen well.

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value: This is done to see instant effects. You can skip restarting explorer from settings and then, to see changes you should restart explorer yourself by (TaskManager\Log Out and Relog In\Restarting Windows\...).
